    Found: [A#1234|567]
    Found: [B#1234|567]
    Found: [C#1234|567]

I&#39;m assuming here that your `Pattern` has specific restrictions:

 - Starts with `[`
 - Followed by **one** upper-case non-accented letter
 - Followed by `#`
 - Followed by any number of digits
 - Followed by `|`
 - Followed by any number of digits
 - Followed by `]`

